sell the new single-chip Vaxen (not that we could really have used
them, ...), so I asked the salesdroid about the possibility of a
single-chip KI10 equivalent. He just about swallowed his tongue, but
claimed he'd "Ask about it". Good thing I didn't hold my breath.

