(I think) could talk about why they picked that approach to 
the implementation lanaguage.  Sara was there, too, but I don't 
know if she was in that part of the planning stages.  I was a
mere Tape Prep type then, so I usually got the info at the
other end of the development cycle.  I do remember that the
work was getting done on 3-5.

